'''重返古战场'''（{{lang-en|''Battlefield Detectives''}}）是一个[[历史频道|历史频道]]2003年至2006年播出的[[纪录片|纪录片]]系列。此节目关注于战役本身，借助于现代科技来探讨历史上的著名战役成败的原因<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/battlefield-detectives/194633 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-03-12 |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219011524/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/battlefield-detectives/194633/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

According to History Television, "This series approaches the perennially interesting topic of famous battles in a fresh and exhilarating way. Focusing on the battlefield itself, each programme takes an important battle telling its story and posing a puzzling central question about the battle that recent scientific research is helping to illuminate - a contemporary journey of discovery and a compelling story from the past."<ref>History Television {{cite web |url=http://www.history.ca/ontv/titledetails.aspx?titleid=68732 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719195543/http://www.history.ca/ontv/titledetails.aspx?titleid=68732 |archivedate=2011-07-19 }} Retrieved 2009-07-24.</ref>

